'''Weeydiin''' ({{lang-en|question}}; {{lang-ar|سؤال}}) sidoo kale loo yaqaano '''Su'aal''' iyo '''Weeydiimo''', waa hab ka mid ah [[luuqad|xidhiidhka luuqada]] taasi oo loo isticmaalo codsiga warbixin iyo faahfaahin ku saabsan meel, qof ama shey. Su'aashu waa nidaamka lagu raadiyo warbixin badan oo sharaxaysa waxa su'aashu ka socoto.<ref>[http://www.accesstoinsight.org/canon/sutta/anguttara/an04-042.html Source for quotation] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060210012407/http://www.accesstoinsight.org/canon/sutta/anguttara/an04-042.html |date=February 10, 2006 }}</ref>
Intaasi waxaa dheer, weeydiinta waxaa ka dambeysa [[jawaab]] oo ah mida ka warbixineysa su'aasha meeshaas taala.
==Ereyga==
Si la mid ah ereyo badan oo ku jira [[Af-Soomaali|luuqada Soomaaliga]], ereyga ''Su'aal'' waxaan ka soo xiganay [[Af-Carabi|luuqada Carabiga]] ereyga "سؤال". Sida saxda ah, ereyga '''Weydiin''' ama '''Weydiimo''' ayaa ah mid Af-Soomaali sax ah.<ref>
